    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "Alani Chicken soup is a quick and easy stew made with very few spices. Alani soup is supposed to be mildly spicy." 
    },
	{
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "It is a healthy soup rich in protein and easily digestive minerals, including calcium. Chicken soup is also considered as one of the best home remedies for common cold. It also helps in boosting immune system and aids digestion." 
    }
