      "procedureSteps": [
        {
          "stepDescription": "Make a fine paste of ginger, garlic, green chillies and coriander leaves. Use this paste to marinate chicken along with turmeric, salt and lemon juice. Let it rest for minimum 2 hours.",
          "stepImages": [
            {
              "ImageUrl": "step_1_1.JPG",
              "ImageAltText": ""
            },
            {
              "ImageUrl": "step_1_2.JPG",
              "ImageAltText": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "stepDescription": "In a pressure cooker, heat oil. Add the bay leaf, cinnamon, cloves, coriander seeds, green and black cardamom, black pepper and star anise. allow it to sizzle. Add onions and fry till golden brown.",
          "stepImages": [
